it.polimi.se2019.model.map

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.model.map.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    A map is a virtual collection of squares, linked together. In reality, only one square is inserted in this class, cause all square are linked together, and therefore the list of squares can easily be retrived
